## 12. Common Mistakes & Key Takeaways

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Generic opening | Lead with your top achievement |
| No skill matching | Map resume skills to JD requirements |
| Too long | Under 250 words; every sentence earns its place |

| # | Takeaway |
|---|----------|
| 1 | **Structured prompts** produce consistent letters |
| 2 | **Role-based prompting** adds personality |
| 3 | **Skill extraction** improves relevance |
| 4 | **Tone variants** serve different cultures |
| 5 | **Rubric evaluation** makes quality measurable |

